flowchart LR
    App[OpenSlopCommandExecProbe] --> Client[WorkbenchCore CoreDaemonClient]
    Client --> Daemon[core-daemon --serve-stdio]
    Daemon --> Provider[provider-domain]
    Provider --> Codex[codex app-server]
    Codex -->|buffered| Final[final stdout stderr exitCode]
    Codex -->|streaming| Delta[command/exec outputDelta]
    Delta --> Daemon
    Daemon --> Event[codex_command_exec_output_event]
    Event --> Client
    Final --> Daemon
    Daemon --> Result[codex_command_exec_result]
    Result --> Client
